msg: - removing all the traces about enableREST params from axis2.xml (Oh god, how many axis2.xml files we have within all the modules :( ).
enableRESTparam within axis2.xml is not required any more as we support REST by default now. But enableREST property will be used by the client within the code to twist between REST and SOAP calls.
